Class InteractionEvidenceEnricherStatisticsWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer.EnricherStatisticsWriter<I>
      • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer.InteractionEnricherStatisticsWriter<InteractionEvidence>
        • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer.InteractionEvidenceEnricherStatisticsWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, EnricherListener<InteractionEvidence>, InteractionEnricherListener<InteractionEvidence>, InteractionEvidenceEnricherListener, AnnotationsChangeListener<InteractionEvidence>, ChecksumsChangeListener<InteractionEvidence>, ConfidencesChangeListener<InteractionEvidence>, IdentifiersChangeListener<InteractionEvidence>, InteractionChangeListener<InteractionEvidence>, InteractionEvidenceChangeListener, ParametersChangeListener<InteractionEvidence>, XrefsChangeListener<InteractionEvidence>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    InteractionEvidenceImexEnricherStatisticsWriter

    public class InteractionEvidenceEnricherStatisticsWriter
extends InteractionEnricherStatisticsWriter<InteractionEvidence>
implements InteractionEvidenceEnricherListener
    A statistics logger which records changes made by the enricher. Each addition, removal or update is counted and, upon the completion of the enrichment of the object, is logged in either a file of successes or failures depending on the enrichmentStatus.
    Since:
    18/07/13
    Author:
    Gabriel Aldam (galdam@ebi.ac.uk)
